Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.13,0:00:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to sally.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.88,0:00:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I beg your pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.76,0:00:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That would be suicidal!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.39,0:00:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We should at least wait\Nuntil Lady Marrine's troops get here—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.26,0:00:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You would expose\Nthe Margrave of Waldlind to danger, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.18,0:00:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't intend for...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.60,0:00:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I believe that if you and Lady Marrine\Nfought together, we could overcome this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.11,0:00:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And perhaps we could.\NBut what would happen if we failed?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.70,0:00:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Waldlind's Knights-at-Arms are far too slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.66,0:00:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If the enemy gives chase,\Nthey can't flee.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.24,0:00:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, at this rate, it's you who...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.79,0:00:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't belittle me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.17,0:00:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how vast\Nthe enemy forces, I will not lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.25,0:00:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If they're attacking in full force,\Nthat just makes it more convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.35,0:01:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I beg of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.89,0:01:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I beg of you,\Nplease be patient for just a while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.27,0:01:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we're barricaded inside\NCastle Unicorn, we can't get captured so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.86,0:01:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Marrine will definitely turn the tide!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.82,0:01:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Telius.\NWhose contracted mage are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.12,0:01:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Marrine's.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.04,0:01:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I've been sent to serve you, Sir Milza.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.17,0:01:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you've served me well all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.92,0:01:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I've always decided everything on my own,\Nand I've always led the charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.63,0:01:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}But I know there are limits to such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.22,0:01:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}And you taught me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.93,0:01:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Sir Milza.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.27,0:01:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault for lacking talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.02,0:01:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.19,0:01:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My plan was to replace the Eramu mages\Nand usher in the age of the Lords.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.70,0:01:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But apparently he'd sensed\Nthe advent of the age of the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.70,0:02:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I do fall to Theo,\Nit means that this era didn't choose me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.08,0:02:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps soon we'll see an age\Nwhen the people choose their own Lords.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.55,0:02:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I will never acknowledge it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.72,0:02:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When you mobilize,\NI will accompany you, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.74,0:02:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.47,0:04:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.57,0:04:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Dartanian forces are attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.19,0:04:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody, get into position!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.03,0:04:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Send the signal,\Nand notify them of the enemy attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So he's finally coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He'll eventually assault this base as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.42,0:05:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's settle this\Nonce and for all with Prince Milza.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I'd hoped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,First, we'll strike the south!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll slash through the enemy lines\Nand get to Cornaro's base!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.52,0:05:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ignore the fort!\NWe can't afford to waste any time here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we're going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll drive the reinforcements\Nback beyond the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't falter!\NKeep pushing forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.45,0:06:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Withdraw! Withdraw at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.45,0:06:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hoped to distinguish myself here to increase\Nmy influence at the next Lords' summit, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you have against\Nthe Earl of Sistina leading the Treaty?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Only those who come from a long line\Nof eminent Lords are fit to rule as leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And yet the ruler of our Treaty\Ncould soon be Theo Cornaro, a commoner!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Utilizing the power of the masses\Nto win battles has never been done before!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it feel like a new era is coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.65,0:06:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's precisely what terrifies me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.07,0:06:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't see myself in that era.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.83,0:07:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's our next target!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Kilhis army, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're currently led by Baron Jorgo,\Nthe son of the Theater King, Solon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Approximately 1,000 troops!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.09,0:07:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to destroy them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Dartanian forces are headed this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.15,0:07:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there's no stopping them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let me prepare to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Although I'd intended to live a dull life...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don your masks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We shall now become the founder\Nof the Dalaras family, the Lion King!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let the curtain rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.26,0:07:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the leading man?\NWho's playing the minor role?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}That will be revealed\Nwhen the curtain goes down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So they've made it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.98,0:08:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We fought the Dartanian forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.19,0:08:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Number of survivors on our side, 362.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.32,0:08:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Number of enemy soldiers killed, 427.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Dartanian army is powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.87,0:09:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Prince Milza's battle strategy\Nis quite flexible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He might've decided that\Nit would be better to defeat Sir Theo first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pursue Milza!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- So you survived, Sir Selge?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We hastened to join you\Nafter receiving word from Sir Alfred.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.73,0:09:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're planning to pursue Milza,\Nplease let us join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.02,0:09:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's split up and pursue him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.52,0:09:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, we'll take the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.20,0:09:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Milza...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I won't let you kill the man\Nwho'll soon be my Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.05,0:09:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.47,0:10:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As for all the volunteers who showed up,\Nlet's send them away from the base.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.72,0:10:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Milza is a dangerous opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.89,0:10:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting him will lead to many casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.69,0:10:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From here, the Lords and regular Knights\Nwill be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.73,0:10:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I may, sir, this isn't just your battle.\NIt's also ours, the citizens of Altirks battle as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is not Dartania!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please order us to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please give us courage by showing us\Nthat battle flag we've heard so much about!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.25,0:10:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Please!\N- Sir Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.26,0:10:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you all have something\Nthat you really want to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.37,0:11:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To take back Altirk...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fight together!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.43,0:11:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our target is the Earl of Sistina, Theo Cornaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.35,0:11:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we can defeat him, victory will be ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.78,0:11:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Follow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is this devious, underhanded strategy\NSiluca Meletes' handiwork?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.67,0:11:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that devilish woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:11:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.72,0:12:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you through!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.39,0:12:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such impudence!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.64,0:12:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to guide you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.10,0:12:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to the afterlife!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.19,0:12:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...it's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.01,0:12:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.77,0:12:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.03,0:13:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Theo Cornaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fight me one-on-one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.01,0:13:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not! If you end up losing,\Nyou'll have played right into Milza's hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about the future of the Treaty,\Nand the future of the Continent?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.35,0:13:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll all work out somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.68,0:13:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you to accept a duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.69,0:13:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is also who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.11,0:13:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,please make sure to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.12,0:13:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That might be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.74,0:13:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's definitely not like me to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.25,0:13:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.59,0:14:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I also have no intention of losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.39,0:14:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you've said your goodbyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.08,0:15:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This was given to me as a reward\Nfor capturing the Black Witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.75,0:15:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hear it was made of metal\Nfrom another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.25,0:15:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then all I have to do is chop off your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.89,0:15:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you refuse to attack me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because this is how I fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.86,0:15:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.63,0:16:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}You're weaker now than you were that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.51,0:16:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.88,0:16:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Until now, you only used\Nthe power of your Crest for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.85,0:16:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But in order to take over Altirk, you've bestowed\Nsubjugated Crests on scores of your men.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And your Crest has lost power accordingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can still continue fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you're already out of breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your Crest's protection\Nis preserving your strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.28,0:16:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but you're almost at your limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know when to shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.43,0:16:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I've won.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you've been defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.73,0:17:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Just take a look around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}None of your men are fighting anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.61,0:17:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.57,0:17:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Earl of Sistina!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.12,0:17:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will never be defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to ask, as a formality.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.57,0:17:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your Crest, or your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.65,0:17:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will never beg for my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.62,0:17:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.47,0:18:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Milza!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.64,0:18:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If only...\NIf only I had more talent to offer you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Both you and I did everything we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.44,0:18:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter how much knowledge\Nwe utilize and formulate strategies,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.07,0:18:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that doesn't mean everything will go to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.99,0:18:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It all depends on whether\Nwe have destiny on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.41,0:18:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I still wanted Sir Milza to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I shall accompany you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.22,0:19:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've taken back the Crest\Nof the Earl of Altirk, Villar Constance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.44,0:19:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad you're all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.45,0:20:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to make you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.66,0:20:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.79,0:20:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything like that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.63,0:20:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It won't happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.51,0:20:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because there's no one else left\Nthat I want to take down myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.38,0:21:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After battling Theo Cornaro, the Earl of Sistina,\Nin a dual, Sir Milza met a heroic death.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't he wait for our forces to arrive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.02,0:21:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He must've determined that there would be\Nno reinforcements from Dartania or Starck.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.56,0:21:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And even if we joined them, our forces alone\Nwould not guarantee victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.99,0:21:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, he would have\Nexposed you to danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he has belittled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.95,0:21:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.00,0:21:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now that Sir Milza is dead,\Nthere's no reason to continue our advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.25,0:21:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All forces, change course!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.92,0:21:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading back north immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.17,0:21:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Before the Treaty can start pressuring us,\Nwe'll finish off the Earl of Le Couleurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.35,0:21:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Milza...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.40,0:21:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.07,0:22:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TWO HEROES
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.99,0:23:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EPISODE 18\NLEADER
